msgstr "Örnekler:"

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"In your CMP, block the BimBeau Privacy Analytics advanced stats script until "
"the Statistics or Analytics purpose is accepted."
msgstr ""
"CMP’nizde, İstatistik veya Analitik amacı kabul edilene kadar BimBeau "
"Privacy Analytics gelişmiş istatistik betiğini engelleyin."

#: src/admin/panels/SettingsPanel.js
msgid ""
"Advanced stats are disabled. BimBeau Privacy Analytics will only use "
"essential stats."
msgstr ""
"Gelişmiş istatistikler devre dışı. BimBeau Privacy Analytics yalnızca temel "
"istatistikleri kullanacak."

